        • appendNamedParameters
          boolean appendNamedParameters
          This flag controls if passed named params should be appended to the map in AbstractMatcher.replaceParameters(Map, Map) and will be accessible in ResultConfig. If set to false, the named parameters won't be appended.

          This behaviour is controlled by StrutsConstants.STRUTS_MATCHER_APPEND_NAMED_PARAMETERS
